Social Media App
Overview
This is a social media application that allows users to create profiles, share posts, interact with other users, and follow content they are interested in. The app provides features like posting text and images, commenting, liking, and following other users. It is designed to be interactive and user-friendly, making it easy to connect with others.

Features
User Authentication: Register and log in securely with email or username.
Profiles: Create and edit personal profiles, including profile picture and bio.
Posting: Share content, such as text updates and images, with followers.
Interactions: Like, comment, and share posts.
Followers: Follow other users to stay updated on their activity.
Notifications: Receive updates about likes, comments, and follows.
Real-time Updates: Live notifications and updates on the timeline.
